 
💡 Lovable Build Prompt — GlobalPulseWorld.xyz
We’re building GlobalPulseWorld.xyz, the official home of Pulse chat — The World’s 24-Hour Conversation.
This is the front page of a global movement to map humanity’s heartbeat through real-time conversation.
At its core is Pulsechat.online, the world’s first chat that resets every 24 hours — a digital pulse that reflects how humanity feels, one day at a time.
The website should inspire visitors to join this experiment in collective emotion and communication, while previewing the broader Global Pulse ecosystem that’s evolving around it.
 
🧭 Purpose and Mood
•	Feel: clean, bold, emotional minimalism (Apple × Notion aesthetic).
•	Mood: alive, human, global — with a subtle heartbeat or countdown animation.
•	Emphasis: conversation, emotion, renewal, and global connection.
•	Tone: visionary yet simple — the world’s daily reset in a single breath.
 
🧩 Core Requirements
Framework: Next.js + TailwindCSS, deployed on Vercel.
Domain: globalpulseworld.xyz
Pages:
1.	Home (/) — Core experience and CTA to join Pulsechat.
2.	About (/about) — Mission, vision, and philosophical roots.
3.	Roadmap (/roadmap) — Evolution of the ecosystem, including “coming soon” utilities.
 
