🧠 Messaging Tone
Use natural, emotional, global language.
Mix the words emotion, chat, and conversation interchangeably — never cold or corporate.
Avoid overemphasizing crypto, metrics, or tech — this is about humanity first.
Highlight the 24-hour reset and “world’s first chat that restarts daily” as the key innovation.
 
